rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係大家可以放心入手"},{"pid":"4e46600b0d6c7e78be109afe4dae62d9d8bd22e6","tid":1615570,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:56:17.000Z","msg":"10.2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545663ff6e1c7babc70867650449a25b400ed3f1","tid":1615570,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:30:14.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"9a50a0a01d1a2631a7a1be815654114482515611","tid":1615570,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb6f4ad274c43694fd539e31107fda7f8ff13749","tid":1615570,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:31:37.000Z","msg":"燒山又燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家升到1:10啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:57:51.000Z","msg":"唔好同燒山拜年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/no